{"tid":2162888,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"泛民今日不拒絕委任之六國論","createTime":"2020-08-18T10:59:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T11:04:53.000Z","uid":45975,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9109a0372edf10755e518d1cae1c0e3568a099a6","tid":2162888,"uid":45975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T10:59:01.000Z","msg":"今日割五城，明日割十城，然後得一夕安寢。起視四境，而秦兵又至矣。然則諸侯之地有限，暴秦之慾無厭，奉之彌繁，侵之愈急。故不戰而強弱勝負已判矣。至於顛覆，理固宜然。古人云：&ldquo;以地事秦，猶抱薪救火，薪不盡，火不滅。&rdquo;此言得之。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190808/59f47b5eac344bd882cd169a5bdf09c1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fimages%2F20190808%2F59f47b5eac344bd882cd169a5bdf09c1.png&h=7bd1d1ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"25cd14b0c8c1179926e8410f0da1df373a907a8a","tid":2162888,"uid":198503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T11:04:53.000Z","msg":"nice  simplified Chinese"}]}